<db:anchor xml:id="qt6-add-repc-sources"/>
<db:para>This command was introduced in Qt 6.2.</db:para>
<db:section xml:id="synopsis">
<db:title>Synopsis</db:title>
<db:programlisting language="cpp" role="bad">qt_add_repc_sources(&amp;lt;TARGET&amp;gt; rep_files)

qt6_add_repc_sources(&amp;lt;TARGET&amp;gt; rep_files)
</db:programlisting>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="description">
<db:title>Description</db:title>
<db:para>Runs <db:link xlink:href="qtremoteobjects-repc.xml">repc</db:link> and generates <db:link xlink:href="qtremoteobjects-source.xml">Qt Remote Objects Source</db:link> header files based on the given <db:code>rep_files</db:code>. Adds the generated files to <db:code>&lt;TARGET&gt;</db:code>.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="examples">
<db:title>Examples</db:title>
<db:programlisting language="cpp">qt6_add_repc_sources(directconnectserver
    simpleswitch.rep
)
</db:programlisting>
<db:para>The generated file(s) will be of the form <db:code>rep_&lt;replica file name&gt;_source.h</db:code>, in this case <db:code>rep_simpleswitch_source.h</db:code></db:para>
</db:section>
